You all right? Hold on.

1072
01:26:38.760 --> 01:26:39.866
Get out of the car.

1073
01:26:39.890 --> 01:26:41.656
I could've handed you to them.
And they find me now they...

1074
01:26:41.680 --> 01:26:43.826
