1121
01:29:22.390 --> 01:29:24.050
We'll make her testify.

1122
01:29:24.720 --> 01:29:26.866
I know how this sounds.

1123
01:29:26.890 --> 01:29:28.060
but you call me

1124
01:29:28.230 --> 01:29:29.850
on my cellular.

1125
01:29:30.230 --> 01:29:31.900
And you be careful.

1126
01:29:32.900 --> 01:29:34.110
They...

1127
