be intercepted.

1171
01:32:55.310 --> 01:32:58.376
Those calls you made
to B of A. France.

1172
01:32:58.400 --> 01:33:02.070
B of A. France. Switzerland.
you were talking to us.

1173
01:33:02.400 --> 01:33:03.756
You were talking to us.

1174
01:33:03.780 --> 01:33:05.836
Filled in the blanks.
Access codes.

1175
01:33:05.860 --> 01:33:08.086
passwords. access
codes. passwords...

1176
01:33:08.110 --> 01:33:12.176
Stuff even your lawyer didn't have.
Stuff even your lawyer didn't have.

1177
01:33:12.200 --> 01:33:14.370
We have it now so we're done.

1178
01:33:27.970 --> 01:33:29.430
Bye. Nicholas.

1179
01:35:54.530 --> 01:35:56.030
Things have happened

1180
01:35:56.740 --> 01:35:59.120
and it's important that...
Shh. shh. shh!

1181
