1192
01:36:42.870 --> 01:36:45.566
And I just need enough
to get out of here.

1193
01:36:45.590 --> 01:36:49.276
Oh. we'll help with the local law
enforcement if you wanted to bother.

1194
01:36:49.300 --> 01:36:52.760
As far as money is concerned.
can I make a suggestion?

1195
01:36:53.930 --> 01:36:55.850
You say you were mugged?

1196
01:36:56.510 --> 01:36:58.770
And they didn't take that watch?

1197
01:37:00.850 --> 01:37:03.366
How much is a watch
like that worth?

1198
01:37:03.390 --> 01:37:05.610
A couple of hundred at least.

1199
