1200
01:38:38.570 --> 01:38:40.030
Excuse me?

1201
01:38:41.160 --> 01:38:43.620
Can I have your
attention. please?

1202
01:38:48.170 --> 01:38:49.630
Thank you.

1203
01:38:50.800 --> 01:38:54.050
Anybody here going to San Francisco?
I need a ride.

1204
01:38:57.050 --> 01:38:59.760
I've got $18 and 70...

1205
01:39:00.140 --> 01:39:01.680
78 cents

1206
01:39:03.140 --> 01:39:05.230
for a ride to San Francisco.

1207
01:39:10.980 --> 01:39:12.360
Anybody?

1208
01:41:00.010 --> 01:41:01.800
Keep the change. Thanks. pal.

1209
01:41:05.600 --> 01:41:08.850
Conrad Van Orton. Could you
