Pleasure to meet you. Where's my brother?

1214
01:41:23.830 --> 01:41:25.176
Will you come with me. sir?

1215
01:41:25.200 --> 01:41:27.160
Wait a minute. is there trouble?

1216
01:41:28.330 --> 01:41:30.870
Sir. this is a private
matter for you.

1217
