in case anyone came.

1224
01:42:02.660 --> 01:42:04.740
It's a hospital in Napa. sir.

1225
01:42:05.950 --> 01:42:07.580
I'm terribly sorry.

1226
01:42:24.800 --> 01:42:27.640
Elizabeth. I need
to borrow your car.

1227
01:42:28.560 --> 01:42:29.680
Nickie.

1228
01:42:30.730 --> 01:42:32.770
what happened to you? I mean...

1229
01:42:33.770 --> 01:42:36.110
Look at you. Look at me.
What happened. I...

1230
