you don't tell him you talked to me.
You lie to him.

1238
01:42:59.210 --> 01:43:02.050
And whatever else happens
before he speaks...

1239
01:43:02.300 --> 01:43:03.930
Okay. coffee.

1240
01:43:04.220 --> 01:43:05.906
English muffin.

1241
01:43:05.930 --> 01:43:07.600
and your water.

1242
01:43:08.260 --> 01:43:09.930
This bottle

1243
