Yeah. I opened it.

1244
01:43:12.390 --> 01:43:15.036
I don't want an opened bottle.
I want an unopened bottle.

1245
01:43:15.060 --> 01:43:18.440
I don't want ice in the glass.
I want just a glass.

1246
01:43:18.860 --> 01:43:20.190
please.

1247
01:43:24.360 --> 01:43:25.870
Nickie. talk to me.

1248
01:43:26.030 --> 01:43:27.620
You're scaring me.

1249
01:43:28.490 --> 01:43:30.200
I don't even know
what you're saying.

1250
01:43:30.370 --> 01:43:32.580
I'm sorry. Liz. I don't mean it.
I'm sorry.

1251
01:43:35.540 --> 01:43:39.300
You know. I've been thinking
the last couple of days.

1252
01:43:39.420 --> 01:43:42.010
I've had some spare time.

1253
01:43:45.550 --> 01:43:47.470
And I wanted to tell you that

1254
01:43:49.390 --> 01:43:51.770
I understand why you left me.

1255
01:43:52.680 --> 01:43:55.020
And I know that I resented it.

1256
01:44:00.360 --> 01:44:02.400
I want to apologize to you

1257
01:44:03.950 --> 01:44:05.660
