1258
01:44:06.360 --> 01:44:07.820
and not being there.

1259
01:44:08.780 --> 01:44:10.596
And I hope that you
can forgive me.

1260
01:44:10.620 --> 01:44:13.346
You're tired.
You've been on the go for days.

1261
01:44:13.370 --> 01:44:15.580
There's nothing to forgive.
Then.

1262
01:44:15.710 --> 01:44:17.080
