1263
01:44:17.670 --> 01:44:20.090
The onset of a
migraine headache.

1264
01:44:20.250 --> 01:44:23.986
If this sounds all too familiar.
relief is here at last.

1265
01:44:24.010 --> 01:44:26.566
Oh no. you bastards.

1266
01:44:26.590 --> 01:44:29.786
Taggarene. For nearly a decade.
doctors have been prescribing...

1267
01:44:29.810 --> 01:44:31.680
