1268
01:44:33.350 --> 01:44:38.206
Taggarene is strong medicine for headaches.
toothaches. muscle fatigue. joint pains...

1269
01:44:38.230 --> 01:44:39.876
He's an actor.

1270
01:44:39.900 --> 01:44:42.900
So if you trust your
doctor. trust Taggarene.

1271
01:44:44.450 --> 01:44:46.530
He's an actor on television.

1272
01:44:49.030 --> 01:44:50.700
Can't explain now.

1273
01:44:51.450 --> 01:44:53.160
Can I borrow your Yellow Pages?

1274
01:45:16.850 --> 01:45:20.650
New Moon Cafe.
best in Chinatown.

1275
01:45:22.320 --> 01:45:24.126
Get out of the car. fucker.

1276
01:45:24.150 --> 01:45:26.086
Open the door and
leave it running.

1277
01:45:26.110 --> 01:45:27.176
You're making a mistake here.

1278
01:45:27.200 --> 01:45:30.596
Get the fuck out of the car.

1279
01:45:30.620 --> 01:45:33.330
I am extremely fragile

1280
01:45:33.910 --> 01:45:35.250
right now.

1281
01:45:44.510 --> 01:45:47.840
New Moon Cafe.

1282
01:45:48.340 --> 01:45:50.826
He does commercials. Do you know
how many customers we have?

1283
01:45:50.850 --> 01:45:52.116
Hundreds. thousands.

1284
01:45:52.140 --> 01:45:55.890
I know he ordered from you.
He went to Montgomery Street. 1010...

1285
01:45:57.730 --> 01:45:59.496
Is there anybody here
that can help me?

1286
01:45:59.520 --> 01:46:03.780
He's an actor. He's like one of these
people you have here up on your...

1287
01:46:16.250 --> 01:46:17.870
Hey! Why are you
taking my picture?

1288
01:46:19.750 --> 01:46:22.226
We were hoping he
could audition today.

1289
01:46:22.250 --> 01:46:24.526
He'd really be perfect
for this part.

1290
01:46:24.550 --> 01:46:26.736
Oh. this will break his heart.

1291
01:46:26.760 --> 01:46:29.486
Well is there any place
we can contact him?

1292
01:46:29.510 --> 01:46:32.026
Well. his beeper's
